  "body": "Accepted EIPs:\r\n\r\n - [x] [EIP-152](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/2129): Blake2 compression function F precompile (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19972)\r\n - [x] [EIP-1108](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1108): Reduce alt_bn128 precompile gas costs (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19904)\r\n - [x] [EIP-1344](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1344): ChainID opcode (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19921)\r\n - [x] [EIP-1884](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1884): Repricing for trie-size-dependent opcodes (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19743)\r\n - [x] [EIP-2028](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-2028): Calldata gas cost reduction (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19931)\r\n - [x] [EIP-2200](https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/pull/2200): Rebalance net-metered SSTORE gas cost (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19964)\r\n\r\nMaintenance stuff:\r\n\r\n - [x] Define the Istanbul fork chain config (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19904)\r\n - [x] Integrate Istanbul meta fork config with individual EIPs (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19993)\r\n - [x] Define `--istanbul.override` flag to support last minute delay (https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/20004)\r\n - [ ] Integrate Istanbul into Puppeth\r\n   - https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19926 - need the chain specs for Parity, need to finalize everything before letting people enable it",
